To integrate the react app into Cordova app, follow these instructions:

1.  Delete all files from <cordova-root-dir>/www directory.
2.  Edit the file <react-root-dir>/src/index.js to wrap the main logic
    inside a function to call it after deviceready CordovaEvent.
3.  Edit <react-root-dir>/public/index.html file to include cordova.js
    file.

